<p>
    This website and software was developed by a Real Estate investor who saw the need for there to be a single Nationwide property site to specifically show the nationwide inventory of wholesale and offmarket investment properties to the many investors who simply could not find legitimate properties on a nationwide scale. The ultimate goal was to connect investment property inventory sources to legitimate investors.
</p>
<p>
<h2>Let Nationwide go to work for you</h2>
<h3>Increase your property exposure and interest</h3>
	Nationwide will market your homes on our site as well as the sites of our partners, increasing your exposure and ability to move your property’s faster and generally for a higher price. This way you can focus on finding more investment properties.
</p>
<h3>Efficient</h3>
<p>
    Your offers will come with full details of the Buyer. Buyers may provide POF’s or may register as premium buyers and Nationwide will verify their ability to purchase. Nationwide will also provide the buyers with the right tools to make each transaction smooth and successful.
</p>
